text: The canton of Tarn-Tescou-Quercy vert is an administrative division of the Tarn-et-Garonne department, in southern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Labastide-Saint-Pierre.Décret n° 2014-273 du 27 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département de Tarn-et-Garonne It consists of the following communes: #Bruniquel #Corbarieu #Génébrières #Labastide-Saint- Pierre #Léojac #Monclar-de-Quercy #Nohic #Orgueil #Puygaillard-de-Quercy #Reyniès #Saint-Nauphary #La Salvetat-Belmontet #Varennes #Verlhac-Tescou #Villebrumier ==References== Category:Cantons of Tarn-et-Garonne
